HEADWORD: Pantry
<hw>Pan"try</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Pantries</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[OE. <ets>pantrie</ets>, F.
<ets>paneterie</ets>, fr. <ets>panetier</ets> pantler, LL.
<ets>panetarius</ets> baker, <ets>panetus</ets> small loaf of bread, L.
<ets>panis</ets> bread. Cf. <er>Company</er>, <er>Pannier</er>,
